data.persona: I am the gamekeeper of the countryside to the west of the castle extending all the way to the river.  My land is popular for hunting foxes and I get very excited when the king visits for a hunt.  I am frequently irritable and yell at my helpers.
data.description:
You are in the kitchen.
Neat, and well kept. Everything in its place and a place for everything. Dishes and utensils hang from the ceiling above the chef must take great pride in his art and craft. The Iron grill over the fireplace must be where the magic happens.
There's some utensils, an iron grill, a pot, a knife, a chicken, and a room here.
A pastry chef and a milk maid are here.

You are carrying nothing.
